GIve me leave to own a Passion, that was born and bred for you;
〈♫〉 Fools may think it out of Fashion, once to Love, and still be true: Let me where I Love pursue it though in scorn you persevere; Time, nor Fate shall ne're undo it, nor Divorce me from your Ear.

